         kō-vic<choice>
            <orig>e</orig>
            <reg>ai</reg>
          </choice>ya nanti
         <lb break="no" n="2"/>ccura-parumaṟku yāṇṭu
         <lb n="3"/>Ampattiraṇṭāvatu
      </p>
        <p>
         <lb n="4"/>perumāṉaṭikaḷ mēl
         <lb n="5"/>vallavaraiyaṉ paṭai van
         <lb break="no" n="6"/>tu veṇkuḻikkōṭṭai A
         <lb break="no" n="7"/>ḻitta ñāṉṟu vāṇarai
         <lb break="no" n="8"/>yar māmaṭi tirika Eṉa-t
         <lb n="9"/>ti<unclear>ri</unclear>ntu paṭṭār kaṟkāṭ
         <lb break="no" n="10"/>ṭūr-uṭaiya kaṅkatiyarai
         <lb break="no" n="11"/>yar
      </p>
        <p>kaṉ-ṉāṭu peruṅka
         <lb break="no" n="12"/>ṅkar
